query: SELECT e.id, e.name, e.specialization, et.id as targetId, et.targetType, et.customName, et.targetValue, et.currentValue, et.baseValue, et.month, et.year, et.status FROM employees e LEFT JOIN employeeTargets et ON e.id = et.employeeId WHERE e.name LIKE '%غادة%' ORDER BY et.month, et.targetType;
